      ## Twitter

  .span10
    :markdown
      You can watch us on twitter by following [@fusefabric](http://twitter.com/fusefabric) or alternatively searching for [fusefabric](http://search.twitter.com/search?q=fusefabric) or the [#fusefabric](http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23fusefabric) tag.

      If you find something you like or don't like in Fuse Fabric please do tweet it (with fusefabric or #fusefabric in the text) or lets chat about it on the [mailing list](http://groups.google.com/group/fusefabric)

